   NOVELTY - The rubber belt is covered and packages semiconductive endless rubber belt (1) of several same shapes. The semiconductive endless rubber belt has a release layer on the surface. The cylindrical structures (2) are inserted into both ends inside the covered semiconductive endless rubber belt in a state with the center axis parallel to the width direction.    USE - For semiconductive endless rubber belt such as transfer belt and conveying belt used in electrostatic-image-development type image forming device.    ADVANTAGE - The friction damage to the semiconductive endless rubber belt is prevented.    DESCRIPTION OF DRAWING(S) - The figure shows a perspective view of the package unit.    Semiconductive endless rubber belt (1)    Cylinder structure (2) 